hints.content: When we skip count by hundreds,  we add $100$ to each number as we count.

Aubrey started with $758$,  so we need to add $100$ more to $758$.

$758 + 100 = 858$

The next number Aubrey will say is $858$.

Aubrey is still skip counting by hundreds so we need to add $100$ to $858$.

$858+ 100 = 958$

The next number Aubrey will say is $958$.
